des:
This skill is part of Mini Games

It's finally time to build your own PANCAKE EMPIRE!

Earn the most pancakes the world has ever seen. In this game, you need to manage your pancake demand and get upgrades for your pancake empire.

There are loads of upgrades available to boost your Pancakes per second. Upgrades include:

Granny
Chicken
Cow
Pancake Robots
Pancake Tech
Pancake Currency
Pancake Books
Pancake Factory
Pancake Wizard

Each Upgrade will increase your pancakes earned per second. Get the most pancakes per second and climb the Pancake Empire leaderboard!

This skill is part of Mini Games. If you open it, it will tell you to play Mini Games

Have Fun!
